\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {5}{\ignorespaces Cross-dataset validation on the Skoltech Anomaly Benchmark (SKAB). The Base TCN and Full Enhanced models are trained from scratch on the SKAB anomaly-free recording (9405 rows, 1\,Hz, eight sensor channels). Detection thresholds are calibrated on a held-out validation slice (95\textsuperscript  {th} percentile of anomaly score, anomaly fraction = 33.8\%) and applied unchanged to the anomaly-rich test slice (anomaly fraction = 36.1\%). Numerics are loaded verbatim from \texttt  {research\_outputs\_full/tables/skab\_metrics.csv}; no value in this table is hardcoded in the paper source.}}{17}{table.caption.10}\protected@file@percent }
